<plot>This late-evening news program typically followed the late 11 o'clock local news on most stations. Hosted by news veteran Charles Kuralt, and with support from reportes Leslie Stahl and Edie Magnus, this show provided viewers with a recap of the day's news stories, from politics and scandals to international crises and natural disasters.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?034386</url></doc>
